dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast : volume three
dct_description_sm: Index for maps of Como, Spring Lake and Sea Girt; Manasquan; Point Pleasant; Bay Head; Mantoloking; Chadwick ; Lavallette and Ortley; Sea Side Park; Island Heights; and Toms River. Index sheet; map sheets foldered separately under names of towns.
